NT><FONT face=宋体>《北方新报》（作者：牟野）《内蒙古</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT><FONT face=宋体>高招录取结束&nbsp;本专科共录取</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">165740</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人》：内蒙古自治区</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT><FONT face=宋体>年普通高校招生录取工作于</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">8</FONT><FONT face=宋体>月</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">4</FONT><FONT face=宋体>日结束，本专科共录取考生</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">165740</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人。其中，本科批次录取考生</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">94897</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人，高职高专批录取考生</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">70843</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">根据以上数据计算，内蒙古自治区</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">2012<FONT face=宋体>年普通高校招生本科一批占招生总量的比重约为：</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">20822<FONT face=宋体>人</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">÷165740人</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">=12.56%</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">内蒙古自治区2012年普通高等学校招生录取一批本科占招生总量的比重约为12.56%</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=