ace=宋体>人</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">，</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">实际招生<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">30841</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">，</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">增加<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1126</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人、增幅</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3.79%</FONT><FONT face=宋体>。其中</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">，</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">文史类实际招生<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">5917&nbsp;</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">，</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">增招<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">391</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">；</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">理工类实际招生<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">24924</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">，</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">增招<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">865</FONT><FONT face=宋体>人。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FO