face=宋体>万人，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">二本批次共录取新生近<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">5.07</FONT><FONT face=宋体>万人，三本批次共录新生</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1.8</FONT><FONT face=宋体>万余人，加上本科提前批、贫困地区专项计划批等其他本科批次，今年本科批次总共录取新生</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">10.5</FONT><FONT face=宋体>万人。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">2012<FONT face=宋体>年</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">8</FONT><FONT face=宋体>月</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1</FONT><FONT face=宋体>日，</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">青年人网讯</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">《</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">2012<FONT face=宋体>年</FONT><A name=baidusnap0></A>广西高职计划招生<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">14</FONT><FONT face=宋体>万人&nbsp;比去年增近</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2.3</FONT><FONT face=宋体>万人</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">》：今年国家和自治区下达的高职高专招生计划数有<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">14</FONT><FONT face=宋体>万余人，比上年增加了近</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2.3</FONT><FONT face=宋体>万人，计划投放量较大，可以说只要考生成绩上线，就不会因为取消补录而“无书可读”。&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">广西壮族自治区<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT><FONT face=宋体>年普通高等学校招生录取总量约为</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">16.06</FONT><FONT face=宋体>万人</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">广西壮族自治区<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT><FONT face=宋体>年普通高等学校招生录取一批本科占招生总量的比重约为</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">12.83%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">2.06<FONT face=宋体>万人</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">/16.06<FONT face=宋体>万人</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">=12.83%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">海南</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">省</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"> </SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \