=\"Times New Roman\">18</FONT><FONT face=宋体>万，录取率远超</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">80%</FONT><FONT face=宋体>。少数民族考生录取率高于汉族考生录取率。</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">23</FONT><FONT face=宋体>日，记者从省招生考试院获悉：今年我省共录取考生</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">18.75</FONT><FONT face=宋体>万人，录取率超过去年。此外，今年我省少数民族考生录取率高于汉族考生录取率。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">暂未查到<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT><FONT face=宋体>年一本录取数据，暂用</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2011</FONT><FONT face=宋体>年数据代替。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">云南省<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2012</FONT><FONT face=宋体>年普通高等学校招生录取一批本科占招生总量的比重约为</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">10.67%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">20000<FONT face=宋体>人</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">/18.75</FONT><FONT face=宋体>万人</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">=10.67%</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">西藏</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold