INSERT INTO uchome_blogfield VALUES('808','83272','a:2:{i:126;s:3:\"的\";i:127;s:6:\"文章\";}','<DIV>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">我看<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>商江</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>及商江的文章</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 15pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">1067<FONT face=宋体>个字符&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">今天偶尔上网，看到博客里有一高人，欣欣然拜读了高人的大作。特写此文以志感想。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;文章的作者叫商江。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;商江何许人也？我不知道。看介绍知道他是大庆广播电视大学的老师。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;商江人怎么样？我也不知道，只知道他在中华心理教育网里有一个博客。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;但是，文如其人，文章写的这么好，人，估计不会差到哪里去。心理学上有所谓<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>产品分析法</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>，就是通过作品去分析人的性格。这里，我没有分析性格的意思，只是想说，人大概是不会错的。商江是一个性情中人，这是我的感觉。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;商江关于教育的论文我看了。他对国家的教育制度有许多的感想，许多的感悟，许多的感慨，让我这个凡夫俗子非常的感动。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;俗话说，文以载道，历来文章的目的，都有负载<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>的责任。</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>是第一性的，而</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>文</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>仅仅被视为一种负载大道的工具。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\"<FONT face=宋体>道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>有大小之分。关乎</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>江山社稷</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>，谓之</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>大道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>；关于</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>百姓民生</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>，则为</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>小道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;唐宋以降，许多后世文人对&nbsp;<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>务虚</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"&nbsp;</FONT><FONT face=宋体>的</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>大道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>津津有味，一来国家提倡，二来文人高兴。所以各种</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>策论</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>漫天飞舞，承转启合，乐此不疲，文人之于此类文章情有独钟，也游刃有余。文人对于</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>大道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>的兴趣，已经远远超过了</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>小道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>、</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>旁门左道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>或</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>歪门邪道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>。只可惜，国家在</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1905</FONT><FONT face=宋体>年取消了科举，且又经过了五四运动的洗涤，按说这文人的</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>假</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>、文人的</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>大</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>，文人的</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>空</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>应当是有所收敛，毕竟是事过境迁；但事实却完全相反，时代变了，文人的固执，却没有任何的改变。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">文章要议论<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>小道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>。关注时政、议论民生，抨击丑恶，做道德的脊梁，可惜中国有自命不凡的文人对此没有兴趣。提起</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>小道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>，便有一种</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>阉割恐惧</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>，让现今中国的一些文章，脱离了社会，成为花拳秀腿的点缀。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">好文章应当是<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>大道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>与</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>小道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>连通的。为人民谋福祉，看似</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>小道</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>，实乃大道。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;商江的文章，好就好在<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>尚实</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>！旁征博引，说出了教育的真实，给当局参考的同时，也让我们这些后学者看到了教育的良心。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">我感慨，商江从教育现象入手，却也能做成宏篇巨帜，纵横排阖，出手不凡，无论是各地大学竟相建楼是否合适的立论；还是农村教育成本增加，给农民子女受教育带来的问题；以及普通高校招生规模的问题。字字珠玑，关乎中国教育的未来，大哉斯言，真的是善之善哉，道莫大焉。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;商江是一个新博客。我是知道商江的<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>第一人</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>（笑）。</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>江山代有才人出，各领风骚数百年</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">\"</FONT><FONT face=宋体>。</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">商江的学术之树常青，我愿做你永远的读者。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">一个喜欢看商江文章的老师&nbsp;海之恋&nbsp;于江苏南京</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">2006<FONT face=宋体>年</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">12</FONT><FONT face=宋体>月</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">9</FONT><FONT face=宋体>日</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">中华心理博客&nbsp;海之恋的个人空间</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">http://space.xinli110.com/981/viewspace-430</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; F