<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 108pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">我在著作勒口用的“作者简介”：</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">商江，男，</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">1953</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">年出生，黑龙江省大庆市人，</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">1974</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">年毕业于大庆师范学校（</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">2004</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">年更名为大庆师范学院）数学专业，</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">1985</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">年毕业于黑龙江省大学主考的党政干部基础科（自学考试），</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">1997</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">年毕业于中共中央党校函授学院经济管理专业。职称，经济师。从事教育工作</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">30</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">多年，从经济学角度研究教育问题。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">2002</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">年担任大庆广播电视大学副校长以来，在高等学校学报和期刊杂志发表论文几十篇。已经出版专著</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">7</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">部：《反思中国教育</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">---</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">商江教育论文集》、《评说中国教育</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">---</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">商江教育论文集》、《正视中国教育</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">---</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">商江教育论文选集》、《眺望中国教育</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">---</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">商江教育论文汇集》、《关注中国教育</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">---</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">商江教育论文合集》、</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">《揣摩中国教育</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: \'Verdana\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">—</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">商江教育论文续集》《商江选读</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: \'Verdana\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">&lt;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">宋词三百首</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: \'Verdana\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">&gt;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">》</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">。在全国教育界产生一定影响。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"PADDING-RIGHT: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; PADDING-LEFT: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; PADDING-TOP: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">2011<FONT face=宋体>年</FONT><FONT face=Arial>4</FONT><FONT face=宋体>月</FONT><FONT face=Arial>20</FONT><FONT face=宋体>日，大庆油田图书馆颁发证书：“商江同志：您捐赠的《</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">商江扫描</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">&lt;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">金瓶梅</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">&gt;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; F