\'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">1953</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">年出生，黑龙江省大庆市人，</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">1974</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">年毕业于大庆师范学校（</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">2004</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">年更名为大庆师范学院）数学专业，</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">1985</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">年毕业于黑龙江省大学主考的党政干部基础科（自学考试），</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">1997</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">年毕业于中共中央党校函授学院经济管理专业。职称，经济师。从事教育工作</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">30</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'宋体\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">多年，从经济学角度研究教育问题。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; BACKGROUND: rgb(255,255,255); FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255)\">200