yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">2011</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">年</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">9</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">月</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">11</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">日，</SPAN><SPAN><a href=\"http://home.tripbaba.com/link.php?url=http://epaper.jinghua.cn/html/2011-09/11/content_699325.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">京华时报</SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">(</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">记者黄海蕾</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">)</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">《</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">疯狂英语创始人李阳微博承认家暴向妻子道歉</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">》：</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">近日，微博名为<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">丽娜华的</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">Mom</SPAN><SPAN><a href=\"http://home.tripbaba.com/link.php?url=http://weibo.com/2254494161?zw=news\" target=\"_blank\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">(</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">微博</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">)</SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">”</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">的网友在微博上传多张</SPAN><SPAN><a href=\"http://home.tripbaba.com/link.php?url=http://news.sina.com.cn/s/2011-09-05/115123107290.shtml\" target=\"_blank\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">遭遇家暴</SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">的照片，并称实施家暴的就是<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">疯狂英语</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">”</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">创始人李阳</SPAN><SPAN><a href=\"http://home.tripbaba.com/link.php?url=http://weibo.com/lyce?zw=news\" target=\"_blank\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">(</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">微博</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">)</SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">。沉默多日后，昨天下午，李阳在微博中承认自己曾有家暴行为，并向妻子<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">Kim</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">公开道歉。李阳称，他们夫妻正在接受心理治疗师的专业帮助。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">2011<FONT face=宋体>年</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">9</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">月</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">11</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">日，广州日报（辛浪）《李阳承认家暴&nbsp;道歉之余不忘教英语&nbsp;网友望其好好反省&nbsp;》：在教师节当天下午，李阳用中英双语发微博承认家暴并正式道歉：</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">“<FONT face=宋体>我向</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">KIM</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">正式道歉，我对她实施了家庭暴力，造成了身体和心灵上的严重伤害，对孩子也产生了不良的影响。我也向所有人道歉，我将深刻反省我的行为。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">I&nbsp;wholehearted&nbsp;apologize&nbsp;to&nbsp;my&nbsp;wife&nbsp;Kim&nbsp;and&nbsp;my&nbsp;girls&nbsp;for&nbsp;committing&nbsp;domestic&nbsp;violence.&nbsp;This&nbsp;has&nbsp;caused&nbsp;them&nbsp;serious&nbsp;physical&nbsp;and&nbsp;mental&nbsp;damage<FONT face=宋体>。</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">25<FONT face=宋体>分钟后，他又补充：</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT><FONT face=宋体>按照</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">KIM</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">的要求，我们正在接受心理咨询师的专业帮助。在这里，我再次向大家表示深深的道歉。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">Sorry&nbsp;to&nbsp;let&nbsp;you&nbsp;down!(<FONT face=宋体>抱歉，让你失望了</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">)</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">”</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">当晚</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">7</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">时多，他还转发自己的微博说：</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">“<FONT face=宋体>为了不误导大家的英语，特别更正如下：</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">‘</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">wholehearted</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">’<FONT face=宋体>应该是</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">‘</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">wholeheartedly</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">’<FONT face=宋体>。副词&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">adv.&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">全心全意地。</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">I&nbsp;wholeheartedly&nbsp;believe&nbsp;that&nbsp;you&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;very&nbsp;successful.&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">我坚信你将会非常成功！</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">I&nbsp;will&nbsp;back&nbsp;you&nbsp;up&nbsp;wholeheartedly.&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">我全心全意地支持你。<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">对此，有网友调侃道：<FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT><FONT face=宋体>李阳还真敬业，道歉还不忘教英语。</FONT><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\">土豆网</SPAN><SPAN .=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'\"></SPAN></P>\r\n<P .=p0 .=\"MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt\"